{"tid":1183350,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去不同的國家用不同的卡 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-06-03T00:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T01:27:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38e81cbfe144d67310a28b2965a307b2c3b310c2","tid":1183350,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190524/20685803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F20685803&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOFznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=c95f3bb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F20685803&h=c69c50f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190524/20685803</a><br />\n<br />\n去不同的國家用不同的卡 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190524/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190524%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=51894ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我有一個空的曲奇罐，用來裝不同國家的儲值卡，就像香港八達通卡，當然用途多數不如八達通卡廣泛，在許多國家，這些儲值卡多在乘搭交通工具時使用。<br />\n<br />\n即使同一個國家，也不是一卡通行的，比如高雄用捷運卡，台北則用悠遊卡；澳洲不同省份，使用的卡都不一樣。還有新加坡的、英國的、加拿大的&hellip;&hellip;為方便區分，我在每張卡的背面都貼上小小的貼紙，注明城巿名稱。每次外遊，出門前我都習慣了在曲奇罐中尋找合適的儲值卡。<br />\n<br />\n去日本，我覺得最重要的卡是ETC卡，因為日本的高速公路要收費，收費站分人手收費的現金通道及自動繳費的ETC通道，使用ETC通道方便得多，不用停下來找銀包數錢。不過多數租車公司都提供ETC卡出租服務，預約租車時記得連ETC卡一起租也很方便。<br />\n<br />\n去不同的國家使用當地的卡，說得好聽一點，是尊重別國文化，說得實際一些，是方便自己。除了儲值卡，還要準備一定數量的現金，香港人旅遊成精，知道去甚麼國家要預先在香港兌換現金，去甚麼國家則應該到了當地的兌換店才兌換。我通常在網上自行兌換，臨出發去銀行取。雖然我習慣用信用卡，但總有一些地方、一些店鋪是cash only的，帶一些當地貨幣傍身，方便別人方便自己，是旅行常識。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【有限創意】豺虎北踞 衣冠南渡 (余家強)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n胡適的藏書 (林道群)"},{"pid":"1aba1e8ba457b3bd74ee8555f7c6f7e0e6707528","tid":1183350,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚野廢文嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呃稿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509781db6fd9fa2e97c2d45cd062c608cdf19491","tid":1183350,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1aba1e8ba457b3bd74ee8555f7c6f7e0e6707528","tid":1183350,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚野廢文嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呃稿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"講埋啲我阿媽係女仔嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個世界係有好多白痴嘅。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，連時差都唔識，係咪無讀過書架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28251946&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D28251946%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26page%3D1&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOFznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=e9593b22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28251946&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個又係痴撚線，問烏克蘭同白羅斯係咪洗歐羅，屌你老味，歐盟國家都未係全部用歐羅啦，仲拎呢兩個國家問。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=10276783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D10276783&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOFznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=a8ba7779\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=10276783</a>"}]}